Generating component - 

ng generate component component-name or ng g c component-name

Create component with options -

ng g c component-name --flat -it -is --prefix my --spec false

--flat  - not create component name folder
--it  - not create component template file, use inline html
--is  - not create component style file, use inline css
--prefix - use my in selector ex. my-contact-list
--spec -not create component spec.ts file 

Generating Directive with options- 
ng generative directive directive-name  or ng g d directive-name

ng g d btnConffirm --flat false --prefix my --spec false

--flat false - create folder for directive

Generating Services with options-
ng generate service service_name or ng g s service_name

it will create service but not import in app module

for importing ng g s contactData -m app.module 

--flat, --spec

Generating Pipes with options -

ng generate pipe employeeTtile  or ng g p employeeTtile

--flat, --spec

Generating Class-

ng generate class class_name  or ng g cl class_name

Generating interface-
ng generate interface interface_name or ng g i interface_name


Generating Enumerations-
ng generate enum enum_name or ng g e enum_name

Generating inside Models folder-

ng g cl models/contact
ng g i models/person

Generating Modules-
ng generate module module_name or ng g m admin


Generating routing-
ng new demoApp --routing

Open application in browser-
ng serve -o or ng serve --open


Adding Bootstrap-
npm install --save bootstrap then add css link of bootstrap in angular-cli.json in styles

Adding Font-awesome
npm install --save font-awesome then add css link ofawesome fonts in angular-cli.json in styles

ng serve -o -p 3000

